  "response": "\"Wagle Ki Duniya\" is a classic Indian television series that originally aired on Doordarshan. If you are looking to watch all the episodes of the series, there are several options you can explore:\n\n1. **Doordarshan Archives:** Check if Doordarshan, India's national broadcaster, offers access to its archives. They sometimes provide recordings of popular old shows.\n\n2. **Online Streaming Platforms:** Some streaming platforms might have acquired the rights to the series. Check services like Amazon Prime, Netflix, or Hotstar to see if \"Wagle Ki Duniya\" is available.\n\n3. **YouTube:** Many old TV shows have episodes uploaded by fans or official channels on YouTube. You might be able to find episodes of \"Wagle Ki Duniya\" by searching on YouTube.\n\n4. **DVDs and VCDs:** Look for DVD or VCD collections of the series in online stores like Amazon or Flipkart, or in physical stores that specialize in old television shows.\n\n5. **TV Channels:** Occasionally, television channels that focus on classic programming might air old episodes of \"Wagle Ki Duniya.\"\n\nRemember to always use legal and authorized channels to access content.",
